# Raíz del monorepo: sin package.json; evita lockfile accidental si se ejecuta npm aquí.
/package-lock.json

# --- Node / frontend ---
node_modules/
**/node_modules/

dist/
**/dist/

.vite/
**/.vite/

# --- Variables de entorno (mantener plantillas) ---
.env
/.env
.env.local
**/.env.local
!.env.example
!/.env.example
!**/.env.example

# --- Logs ---
*.log
logs/
**/logs/

# --- Paquetes / backups ---
*.tar.gz
*.tgz

# --- Hyperledger / Explorer: datos locales ---
wallet/
**/wallet/

explorerdb/
**/explorerdb/

# Organizaciones Fabric: NO ignorar organizations/ completo (hay scripts y plantillas versionados).
# Solo artefactos generados (crypto, peers, orderers):
**/organizations/ordererOrganizations/
**/organizations/peerOrganizations/
**/organizations/fabric-ca/ordererOrg/
**/organizations/fabric-ca/org1/
**/organizations/fabric-ca/org2/
**/addOrg3/fabric-ca/org3/

system-genesis-block/
**/system-genesis-block/

channel-artifacts/
**/channel-artifacts/

# --- Claves privadas ---
*_sk
**/*_sk
priv_sk
**/priv_sk

# --- Portal API (SQLite local) ---
web-portal-api/data/
**/portal.db
**/portal.db-*

# --- SO ---
.DS_Store
